title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Ross Tucker about the final week of NFL Preseason. What does this game mean to players on the cusp of making an NFL roster? Nick Wright discusses the situation with Russ and the Lakers. And LA Times writer Gary Klein explains what happened with the Rams and Bengals during their joint practice yesterday.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
